        {
            "title": "系統性基金以創紀錄速度買入股票,增持860億美元:高盛",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Linaol8dBpjX_6D2P1VUNg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA6H0CU_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 根據高盛週四晚間發布的報告,系統性對沖基金在過去一週以前所未有的速度大舉買入股票,增持860億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛表示,這些由演算法驅動的基金(通常稱為CTA)在過去五個交易日買入股票的速度,堪稱\"歷史上最大規模之一\"。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行指出,自4月初市場轉強以來,對沖基金,尤其是系統性交易的基金,一直在買入股票,為全球股市進一步上漲做好部署。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這波買盤激增之際,股市正徘徊在歷史高點附近,並即將連續第三週上漲,投資者正關注可能為中東衝突帶來短期解決方案的進展。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0e6a3d32-ff4d-3f45-8d25-fe309c8ec504-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛強調,CTA在過去一週累積股票的速度,位居有史以來前五大買入速度之列。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行的模型估計,這些趨勢追蹤型投機者可能會繼續買入股票,並可能在未來五個交易日再增持700億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">高盛表示,這種買入強度與2024年8月、2023年11月和2019年9月CTA激進累積股票的情況相似。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E6%80%A7%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E4%BB%A5%E5%89%B5%E7%B4%80%E9%8C%84%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E8%B2%B7%E5%85%A5%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%A8-%E5%A2%9E%E6%8C%81860%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B-125530864.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 21:35:21",
