        {
            "title": "中石化：受戰爭影響原物料價格上揚、CPL推升走高 本業營運有望改善",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0kEAKudImQz5vJdmae8jVg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/abb6e292ecaf5702610de6ccf2d019f1\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E7%9F%B3%E5%8C%96-%E5%8F%97%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%E5%8E%9F%E7%89%A9%E6%96%99%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E4%B8%8A%E6%8F%9A-cpl%E6%8E%A8%E5%8D%87%E8%B5%B0%E9%AB%98-%E6%9C%AC%E6%A5%AD%E7%87%9F%E9%81%8B%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84-123006072.html",
