        {
            "title": "Barclays:恐懼錯失推動股市創新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/a6RCAuwenlClVnuZ1wBDBw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEABU081_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 根據<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Barclays\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Barclays;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Barclays\">Barclays</a>的最新報告,股市攀升至新高主要是因為投資者受到害怕錯失機會的情緒所驅動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">分析師Emmanuel Cau在報告中表示,「恐懼錯失情緒已將股市推至新高」,儘管石油和利率市場發出更為謹慎的信號。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Cau認為股市表現出「對逆境的驚人韌性」,在停火協議公布後,市場情緒受到提振,主要指數回升至戰前水平或更高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國和科技板塊目前領漲,支持該行對美股優於歐洲股票的偏好,而歐洲第一季初步業績顯示消費者面臨壓力。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-8676a496-b103-3262-813e-e82053a58d89-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Barclays重申其「保持冷靜並持有對沖」的策略在衝突期間奏效,此前該行曾表示地緣政治衝擊「通常最終會成為良好的買入機會」。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但Cau也警告稱,市場目前可能定價了過多希望,因為石油價格和債券收益率都「傳達出對戰爭結局更為謹慎的訊息」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該分析師指出,霍爾木茲海峽的干擾仍在繼續,意味著衝突的經濟成本尚未解決。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們確實感覺『容易』的降級收益已經過去了」,Barclays表示,並補充說股市進一步上漲可能需要石油和利率市場確認衝突確實正在緩解。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管如此,倉位仍是一股強大的力量。Barclays此前強調,CTA和對沖基金的去風險化可能引發「強勁的震倉和貝塔反彈」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">雖然部分情況已經發生,但許多風險控制型基金尚未重新加倉,導致它們追趕反彈。在本週與客戶會面後,該行認為「恐懼錯失情緒顯而易見」,大多數人更願意保持投資,因為「無論如何,股市都想上漲」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/barclays-%E6%81%90%E6%87%BC%E9%8C%AF%E5%A4%B1%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E8%82%A1%E5%B8%82%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-115247928.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-17 20:31:00",
